label: Treasure Coast Newspapers
title: Treasure_Coast_Newspapers
exrest: TCPalm is the digital news site for Treasure Coast Newspapers, the largest daily news operation on the Treasure Coast of southeastern Florida. The region encompasses three coastal counties: Martin County, St. Lucie County and Indian River County. Treasure Coast Newspapers publishes three daily print newspapers: The Stuart News, St. Lucie News Tribune and the Indian River Press Journal, as well as the weekly Jupiter Courier. The site was launched by Scripps Howard newspapers in 1996, and has been owned by Gannett since 2016.
